Package com.commander4j.app

The com.commander4j.app package is used to provide application specific functionality whereas com.commander4j.sys is used to provide generic application independent functions.

See: Description

  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    JDialogAbout
    JDialogAbout is a modal dialog box which displays the application name and program version.
    JDialogAssignLabelDataToLine
    Called from the Case Labelling screen once the user has selected the required process order this dialog box will allow the user to send the data to a nominated Production Line.
    JDialogAutoLabellerProperties
    This Dialog box allow you to edit the properties of the Auto Labeler.
    JDialogDataIDProperties
    JDialogDataIDProperties class is used to amend the APP_MATERIAL_DATA_IDS table.
    JDialogMaterialCustomerDataProperties
    The JDialogMaterialCustomerDataProperties edits a customer specific element of data.
    JDialogModuleAlternative
    This Dialog box allow you to assign an alternative report module based on workstation name.
    JDialogPalletRePrintLabel
    The JDialogPalletRePrintLabel class is a Dialog box loaded from the JInternalFramePalletAdmin class which allows a user to reprint a pallet label.
    JDialogQMActivityProperties
    The JDialogQMActivityProperties is part of the Quality Module within the application.
    JDialogQMDictionaryProperties
    The JDialogQMDictionaryProperties class allows you to edit a single record in the APP_QM_DICTIONARY table.
    JDialogQMInspectionProperties
    The JDialogQMInspectionProperties is part of the Quality Module within the application.
    JDialogQMSelectListProperties
    JDialogQMSelectListProperties is used to administer a single record within the APP_QM_SELECTLIST table.
    JDialogQMTestProperties
    The JDialogQMTestProperties is part of the Quality Module within the application.
    JDialogShiftProperties
    JDialogShiftProperties allows you to define shifts.
    JInternalFrameAutoLabellerLines
    The JInternalFrameAutoLabellerLines class allows the user to manage the table APP_AUTO_LABELLER.
    JInternalFrameCustomerAdmin
    JInternalFrameCustomerAdmin class is used to insert/update/delete the APP_CUSTOMER table.
    JInternalFrameCustomerProperties
    JInternalFrameCustomerProperties class is used to update a record in the APP_CUSTOMER table.
    JInternalFrameDataIDAdmin
    JInternalFrameDataIDAdmin class is used to maintain the record in the APP_MATERIAL_DATA_IDS table.
    JInternalFrameDespatch
    JInternalFrameDespatch class allows you to manually build a despatch and confirm it.
    JInternalFrameJourneyAdmin
    The JInternalFrameJourneyAdmin class allows you to administer the APP_JOURNEY table.
    JInternalFrameJourneyProperties
    The JInternalFrameJourneyProperties class allows you to amend the APP_JOURNEY table.
    JInternalFrameLabelHistory
    JInternalFrameLabelHistory is used view the records (print history) in the APP_LABEL_DATA table.
    JInternalFrameLocationAdmin
    The JInternalFrameMaterialLocationAdmin class allows the user to view/edit the table APP_LOCATION table.
    JInternalFrameLocationProperties
    The JInternalFrameMaterialLocationProperties class allows the user to view/edit a single record in the APP_LOCATION table.
    JInternalFrameMaterialAdmin

    The JInternalFrameMaterialBatchAdmin allows the user to view/edit the table APP_MATERIAL_BATCH table.
    JInternalFrameMaterialBatchProperties
    The JInternalFrameMaterialBatchProperties class allows you to update a record in the APP_MATERIAL_BATCH table and is called from the parent form JInternalFrameMaterialBatchAdmin
    JInternalFrameMaterialCustomerDataAdmin
    The JInternalFrameMaterialCustomerDataAdmin is the admin screen for Administering Material Data which is customer specific.
    JInternalFrameMaterialLocationAdmin
    The JInternalFrameMaterialLocationAdmin class allows you to maintain the table APP_MATERIAL_LOCATION.
    JInternalFrameMaterialLocationProperties
    The JInternalFrameMaterialLocationProperties class allows you to edit a record in the table APP_MATERIAL_LOCATION.
    JInternalFrameMaterialProperties
    The JInternalFrameMaterialProperties is the screen for editing the basic code Material Data.
    JInternalFrameMaterialTypeAdmin
    JInternalFrameMaterialTypeAdmin allows you to administer the records held in the APP_MATERIAL_TYPE table.
    JInternalFrameMaterialTypeProperties
    JInternalFrameMaterialTypeProperties allows you edit a record held in the APP_MATERIAL_TYPE table.
    JInternalFrameMaterialUomAdmin
    The JInternalFrameMaterialUomAdmin is the screen for editing the units of measure which exist for the Material.
    JInternalFrameMaterialUomProperties
    The JInternalFrameMaterialUomProperties is the screen for editing a single unit of measure record for a Material in the APP_MATERIAL_UOM table.
    JInternalFrameMHNAdmin
    JInternalFrameMHNAdmin class allows the user to insert/update/delete Master Hold Notices in the APP_MHN table.
    JInternalFrameMHNAssign
    JInternalFrameMHNAssign class allows the user to assign SSCC's (pallets) to a Master Hold Notice in the APP_MHN table.
    JInternalFrameMHNDecisionAdmin
    JInternalFrameMHNDecisionAdmin class allows the user to insert/update/delete the APP_MHN_DECISIONS table.
    JInternalFrameMHNDecisionProperties
    JInternalFrameMHNDecisionProperties class allows the user to edit a single record the APP_MHN_DECISIONS table.
    JInternalFrameMHNProperties
    JInternalFrameMHNProperties class allows the user to edit a single Master Hold Notice in the APP_MHN table.
    JInternalFrameMHNReasonAdmin
    JInternalFrameMHNReasonAdmin class allows the user to insert/update/delete the APP_MHN_REASONS table.
    JInternalFrameMHNReasonProperties
    JInternalFrameMHNReasonProperties class allows the user to edit a single record in the APP_MHN_REASONS table.
    JInternalFramePackLabelPrint
    JInternalFramePackLabelPrint is used to insert records into the APP_LABEL_DATA table and print a case/tray label either directly or via an interface to an external system.
    JInternalFramePalletAdmin
    The JInternalFramePalletAdmin allows you to search the APP_PALLET table which contains a single record for each SSCC.
    JInternalFramePalletHistoryAdmin
    The JInternalFramePalletHistoryAdmin allows you to search the APP_PALLET_HISTORY table which contains a multiple records for each SSCC.
    JInternalFramePalletProperties
    JInternalFramePalletProperties allows you to view/edit all the fields on a pallet record held in the APP_PALLET table.
    JInternalFramePalletSplit
    JInternalFramePalletSplit allows a user to split a pallet into 2 pallets.
    JInternalFrameProcessOrderAdmin
    The JInternalFrameProcessOrderAdmin is used maintaining the APP_PROCESS_ORDER table.
    JInternalFrameProcessOrderLabel
    The JInternalFrameProcessOrderLabel is used for printing a label with a barcode representation of the Process Order Number.
    JInternalFrameProcessOrderProperties
    The JInternalFrameProcessOrderProperties is used editing a record in the APP_PROCESS_ORDER table.
    JInternalFrameProcessOrderResourceAdmin
    The JInternalFrameProcessOrderResourceAdmin class updates the table APP_PROCESS_ORDER_RESOURCE.
    JInternalFrameProcessOrderResourceProperties
    The JInternalFrameProcessOrderResourceProperties class updates the table APP_PROCESS_ORDER_RESOURCE.
    JInternalFrameProductionConfirmation
    The JInternalFrameProductionConfirmation class is used to confirm an already created SSCC.
    JInternalFrameProductionDeclaration
    The JInternalFrameProductionDeclaration class is the main class for creating and printing SSCC's.

    JInternalFrameQMInspectionAdmin

Package com.commander4j.app Description

The com.commander4j.app package is used to provide application specific functionality whereas com.commander4j.sys is used to provide generic application independent functions.
